2026-07-10 02:17:11 India Standard Time | INFO     | NeuroSan:_log:720 - NeuroSan - Arguments: ('generated/sentinel_crisis_command.StreamingChat', "'[SYSTEM CONTEXT — use this in your response: Current Date: Friday, 10 July 2026 | Current Time: 02:17 am IST IST | Location: India]\n\n[PREVIOUS CHAT HISTORY (For Context & Memory)]\nNone\n\n[NEW USER INPUT]\nOur Bangalore procurement team has raised an urgent vendor payment request for a new client onboarding project. We need to purchase 20 Dell laptops (Latitude 5540) at a total invoice value of \u20b92,32,332 from our approved vendor M/s. Rashi Peripherals Pvt. Ltd. The project kick-off is in 3 days and the laptops must be delivered to our Chennai delivery center. The vendor is demanding advance payment before dispatch, but our standard policy requires 30-day credit. The project manager is escalating this to the executive team. We need a cross-functional decision: approve the advance payment exception, assess financial risk, check vendor contract terms, ensure asset tagging compliance, and get HR to coordinate laptop allocation for the new joiners.'")
