essionalism.\n3.  **Partner Alignment:** Before external communication, we will brief our channel partners. They must receive a "partner-first" briefing to ensure they are equipped to handle inquiries from their own stakeholders, maintaining a unified front.\n4.  **Continuous Feedback Loop:** We will track client sentiment and engagement via marketing analytics post-communication to identify any accounts requiring additional "high-touch" intervention.\n\n**Immediate Next Steps:**\n*   **Sales Ops:** Finalize the list of impacted clients by EOD.\n*   **Partner Ecosystem:** Initiate direct outreach to key alliance partners.\n*   **Marketing:** Draft the client communication templates for internal review.\n\nI will oversee these workstreams to ensure alignment and rapid execution.'}
