2026-07-10 22:21:44 India Standard Time | INFO     | nsflow:_log:720 - nsflow - 2026-07-10 22:21:44 - generated/sentinel_crisis_command - INFO - {'otrace': ['Chief_of_Staff'], 'text': 'result from HR_Safety_Agent\nTo ensure your CFO is ready for the earnings call in two hours, please initiate the following coordinated plan immediately.\n\n### 1. Immediate Security & Containment\n*   **IT/Security Team:** Initiate a **remote wipe** and **credential revocation** for the stolen device immediately. Terminate all active sessions (O365, VPN, SaaS) to prevent unauthorized access.\n*   **Access:** Suspend the CFOâ€™s VPN access and physical office badge until the new device is secured.\n*   **Legal:** Ensure a local FIR (First Information Report) is filed at the nearest Mumbai police station for insurance and audit purposes.\n\n### 2. Temporary Device Provisioning (Mumbai Office)\n*   **Hardware Procurement:** Contact the Mumbai Office Manager/IT Lead immediately to secure a "loaner" machine from the local emergency stock.\n*   **Secure Configuration:**\n    *   **MDM Enrollment:** Enroll the device in your company\'s MDM/EDR solution (e.g., Intune/CrowdStrike) to push security policies and VPN profiles.\n    *   **Identity:** Perform an MFA reset. If the CFO\'s mobile device is also missing, issue a temporary hardware security key.\n    *   **Application:** Install the specific earnings call software (e.g., Zoom/Teams/Q4) and verify calendar sync.\n*   **Handover:** Have a trusted IT member deliver the device directly to the CFO. **Do not ship via courier.**\n\n### 3. Readiness Checklist (120-Minute Timeline)\n*   **0:00â€“0:30:** Initiate device wipe, credential revocation, and identify local replacement hardware.\n*   **0:30â€“1:00:** Configure MDM, push security policies, and sync VPN/MFA.\n*   **1:00â€“1:45:** Install earnings software and perform a connectivity test (Camera/Mic/VPN).\n*   **1:45â€“2:00:** Handover to CFO; verify identity; provide emergency contact for the IR team.\n\n### Critical Action:\n**Who is your primary point of contact in the Mumbai office?** Please provide their name or department so I can facilitate direct communication if needed. Ensure a dedicated IT technician is on standby to support the CFO for the duration of the earnings call.'}
