as the Indian DPDPA). If the inventory contains Personally Identifiable Information (PII), it will be masked during my analysis.\n*   **Audit Trail:** Every step taken will be logged to ensure accountability and adherence to your organization\'s security policies.\n\n**How would you like to proceed?** Please let me know your preferred method for accessing the inventory data.'}
