n "Contact Apple Enterprise Sales."\n2.  **Request a Quote:** Use the [Apple Business Quote Request form](https://www.apple.com/in/shop/browse/business/find_store).\n3.  **Call a Major Reseller:** If you need an answer within hours, call the **Enterprise Sales Desk** of a major regional partner (e.g., *Imagine* or *Unicorn* Enterprise division). They hold local inventory and can confirm if 25 units are available for immediate dispatch or if they need to be back-ordered.\n\n### Important Note on "M3 Max" Availability:\nBecause the M3 Max is a high-end configuration, it is often **"Build-to-Order" (BTO)**. If you require specific RAM (e.g., 64GB or 128GB) or Storage configurations, it is unlikely that 25 units are sitting in a local warehouse. You should expect a **2â€“4 week lead time** for BTO configurations.\n\n**Would you like me to draft an email template you can send to a reseller to expedite this request?**'}
