ng is distributed, not concentrated on a single lead.\n3.  **Define "Definition of Done" for Onboarding:** Create a checklist that defines what "fully onboarded" means for Project Titan (e.g., first PR merged, architectural understanding verified). This turns onboarding into a measurable milestone rather than a nebulous phase.'}
