 approval to proceed with the VDI-based \"phased launch\" to preserve the project timeline.\n\n**Next Steps:**\n*   Distribute onboarding communication to all new hires by EOD Friday.\n*   Finalize ITAM inventory audit for immediate deployment.\n*   Execute formal vendor notice of performance failure."}
