2026-07-10 23:18:46 India Standard Time | INFO     | nsflow:_log:720 - nsflow - 2026-07-10 23:18:46 - generated/sentinel_crisis_command - INFO - {'otrace': ['Chief_of_Staff', 'Vendor_Agent'], 'text': 'result from Sourcing_Sub_Agent\nTo verify the status of the payment and shipment for **M/s Rashi Peripherals**, please provide the following details so I can assist you further:\n\n1.  **Order/Invoice Number:** The specific reference number associated with the transaction.\n2.  **Date of Transaction:** When the order was placed or the payment was initiated.\n3.  **Payment Method:** (e.g., NEFT, RTGS, Cheque, Credit/Debit Card).\n4.  **Tracking Reference (if available):** Any AWB (Air Waybill) number or shipment tracking ID provided by the logistics partner.\n\n***\n\n### How to proceed with the verification:\n\n*   **If you are an internal user/employee:** Please provide the **Customer ID or Account Code** for M/s Rashi Peripherals so I can look up the internal ERP or CRM records.\n*   **If you are a vendor/partner:** I recommend checking the **Partner Portal** or reaching out to your designated **Account Manager** at Rashi Peripherals. They typically provide real-time updates via their online dashboard.\n*   **Common Verification Channels:**\n    *   **Payment Status:** Check your bank\'s transaction history or the "Payment Advice" sent to their finance department.\n    *   **Shipment Status:** Use the AWB number on the respective courier\'s website (e.g., BlueDart, Delhivery, TCI).\n\n**Once you provide the specific Order or Invoice number, I can help you draft a follow-up email or guide you on the exact status check procedure for their specific system.**'}
2026-07-10 23:18:47 India Standard Time | INFO     | nsflow:_log:720 - nsflow - 2026-07-10 23:18:47 - generated/sentinel_crisis_command - INFO - {'otrace': ['Chief_of_Staff'], 'text': 'To verify the status of the payment and shipment for **M/s Rashi Peripherals**, please provide the following details so I can assist you further:\n\n1.  **Order/Invoice Number:** The specific reference number associated with the transaction.\n2.  **Date of Transaction:** When the order was placed or the payment was initiated.\n3.  **Payment Method:** (e.g., NEFT, RTGS, Cheque, Credit/Debit Card).\n4.  **Tracking Reference (if available):** Any AWB (Air Waybill) number or shipment tracking ID provided by the logistics partner.\n\n***\n\n### How to proceed with the verification:\n\n*   **If you are an internal user/employee:** Please provide the **Customer ID or Account Code** for M/s Rashi Peripherals so I can look up the internal ERP or CRM records.\n*   **If you are a vendor/partner:** I recommend checking the **Partner Portal** or reaching out to your designated **Account Manager** at Rashi Peripherals. They typically provide real-time updates via their online dashboard.\n*   **Common Verification Channels:**\n    *   **Payment Status:** Check your bank\'s transaction history or the "Payment Advice" sent to their finance department.\n    *   **Shipment Status:** Use the AWB number on the respective courier\'s website (e.g., BlueDart, Delhivery, TCI).\n\n**Once you provide the specific Order or Invoice number, I can help you draft a follow-up email or guide you on the exact status check procedure for their specific system.**'}
