stency and prevent further reputational damage.\\n\\n#### 4. Systemic Remediation\\n*   **Compliance Protocol:** The Legal and IT Ops teams are implementing a \\"Human-in-the-Loop\\" (HITL) requirement for all automated legal/breach notices to prevent recurrence.\\n\\n**Next Steps for Leadership:**\\n*   **Finance:** Confirm the payment clearing status by [Time].\\n*   **Vendor Management:** Report back on the outcome of the high-level call with Rashi Peripherals.\\n*   **Projects:** Finalize the \\"Critical\\" employee list for potential staggered onboarding."}}'}
