ndor, M/s Rashi Peripherals, just halted the shipment of 150 Dell Latitude laptops destined for the new Chennai delivery center. The project kickoff is in 4 days. They claim our SAP system failed to process their advance payment of \u20b918,50,000, and our automated system sent them a threatening legal notice for breach of contract instead. The vendor's CEO has escalated this on Twitter (X), tagging Cognizant. We need an immediate cross-functional resolution to unfreeze the SAP payment, assess the legal damage, handle the PR fallout on social media, and get the laptops delivered on time.'")
